---
---

<style>
  @keyframes holoSpin {
    0% { transform: rotateY(0deg) rotateX(5deg) translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: rotateY(180deg) rotateX(-5deg) translateY(-20px); }
    100% { transform: rotateY(360deg) rotateX(5deg) translateY(0px); }
  }
  @keyframes holoSpinReverse {
    0% { transform: rotateY(360deg) rotateX(5deg) translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: rotateY(180deg) rotateX(-5deg) translateY(-20px); }
    100% { transform: rotateY(0deg) rotateX(5deg) translateY(0px); }
  }
  .hologram-3d {
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }
</style>

<section class="relative w-full bg-[#0a0a0a] py-32 md:py-48 flex justify-center px-6 overflow-hidden" id="philosophy">
  
  <!-- Mystical Background Texture (Overlay) -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox=%220 0 200 200%22 xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%3E%3Cfilter id=%22noiseFilter%22%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=%22fractalNoise%22 baseFrequency=%220.8%22 numOctaves=%224%22 stitchTiles=%22stitch%22/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=%22100%25%22 height=%22100%25%22 filter=%22url(%23noiseFilter)%22/%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>
  
  <!-- Giant faint Javanese character -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-5">
    <span class="text-[400px] md:text-[600px] text-[#C5A059] font-serif leading-none tracking-tighter">ꦏꦂ</span>
  </div>

  <!-- 3D Holographic Wayang (Left) -->
  <div class="absolute left-[-20%] md:left-[-10%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none z-0" style="perspective: 1000px;">
    <div class="hologram-3d relative w-64 h-[400px] md:w-[400px] md:h-[600px] animate-[holoSpin_25s_linear_infinite]">
      <!-- Layers for 3D depth -->
      { [0, 15, 30].map(z => (
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style={`transform: translateZ(${z}px);`}>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 100 200" class="w-full h-full drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(197,160,89,0.8)] mix-blend-screen">
            <path d="M50 10 C75 50, 95 100, 95 150 C95 180, 75 190, 50 190 C25 190, 5 180, 5 150 C5 100, 25 50, 50 10 Z" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <path d="M50 25 C65 60, 80 100, 80 145 C80 170, 65 180, 50 180 C35 180, 20 170, 20 145 C20 100, 35 60, 50 25 Z" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="140" r="25" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <line x1="50" y1="190" x2="50" y2="10" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="160" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <circle cx="70" cy="160" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="100" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      )) }
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3D Holographic Wayang (Right) -->
  <div class="absolute right-[-20%] md:right-[-10%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none z-0" style="perspective: 1000px;">
    <div class="hologram-3d relative w-64 h-[400px] md:w-[400px] md:h-[600px] animate-[holoSpinReverse_25s_linear_infinite]">
      { [0, 15, 30].map(z => (
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style={`transform: translateZ(${z}px);`}>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 100 200" class="w-full h-full drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(197,160,89,0.8)] mix-blend-screen">
            <path d="M50 10 C75 50, 95 100, 95 150 C95 180, 75 190, 50 190 C25 190, 5 180, 5 150 C5 100, 25 50, 50 10 Z" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <path d="M50 25 C65 60, 80 100, 80 145 C80 170, 65 180, 50 180 C35 180, 20 170, 20 145 C20 100, 35 60, 50 25 Z" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="140" r="25" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <line x1="50" y1="190" x2="50" y2="10" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="160" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <circle cx="70" cy="160" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="100" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      )) }
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-[760px] w-full flex flex-col gap-14 md:gap-20 z-10">
    
    <!-- Section Heading -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-6">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 150" class="w-10 h-16 opacity-80 drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(197,160,89,0.5)]">
        <path d="M50 0 C70 50, 100 90, 100 150 L0 150 C0 90, 30 50, 50 0 Z" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="2"/>
        <path d="M50 20 C65 60, 85 95, 85 150 L15 150 C15 95, 35 60, 50 20 Z" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
      </svg>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-[#C5A059] tracking-wider font-serif italic drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(197,160,89,0.3)] mt-2" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
        The Philosophy
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[#A39E93] tracking-[0.5em] text-[10px] md:text-xs uppercase font-light">de Aurimori</p>
      
      <div class="w-[1px] h-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#C5A059]/60 to-transparent mt-4"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Body Text -->
    <div class="text-[#A39E93] text-[16px] md:text-[18px] leading-[2.2] flex flex-col gap-12 font-serif font-light text-center px-4" style="font-family: 'Lora', serif;">
      
      <p class="text-[#F8F5F0]">
        We have always known that the most tender things grow in the hardest ground.
        That the seed does not choose the dark — it simply refuses to let the dark
        be the last word. We build the same way: not against the weight of what has
        been lost, but from inside it.
      </p>

      <blockquote class="relative py-12 my-4 text-[#C5A059] italic text-[22px] md:text-[26px] leading-[1.8] drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(197,160,89,0.2)]">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-32 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C5A059]/50 to-transparent"></div>
        "The earth does not mourn what it buries. It simply waits — 
        patient and unhurried — for what the pressure will make of it."
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-32 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C5A059]/50 to-transparent"></div>
      </blockquote>

      <p>
        Qarun de Aurimori was never built to be admired. It was built to be felt —
        in the pause before a decision, in the silence a well-made thing leaves behind,
        in the strange comfort of standing inside something that does not pretend
        to be more than it is. We do not decorate. We excavate. We go down
        until we find the thing that was always there, waiting beneath the noise
        to be uncovered.
      </p>

      <p>
        Every structure we raise knows it will one day fall. We do not hide this
        from it. We build the knowledge of its own ending into its bones —
        because only what has made peace with impermanence can stand
        without needing to be defended. <br/><br/>
        <span class="text-[#F8F5F0] italic tracking-wide">That is not resignation.
        That is the only kind of strength that has ever lasted.</span>
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 150" class="w-8 h-12 opacity-60 rotate-180 drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(197,160,89,0.3)]">
          <path d="M50 0 C70 50, 100 90, 100 150 L0 150 C0 90, 30 50, 50 0 Z" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" stroke-width="2"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>